"title": "8497: witnessing, approaches to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8497: witnessing, approaches to",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture provides teaching, supported by examples, concerning when believers should witness, the methods they are to use, and the manner of doing it.</p>\n<h2>When and where to witness</h2>\n<h3>In the home and family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:18-Mark5:19\">MRK 5:18–5:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:38-Luke8:39\">LUK 8:38–8:39</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:1-2Kgs5:3\">2KI 5:1–5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:41\">JHN 1:41</a></p>\n<h3>To individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:40-John1:42\">JHN 1:40–1:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:7-John4:26\">JHN 4:7–4:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:30-Acts8:35\">ACT 8:30–8:35</a></p>\n<h3>To assembled groups</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:17\">ACT 17:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:42\">ACT 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:13\">ACT 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:8-Acts19:9\">ACT 19:8–19:9</a></p>\n<h2>Methods of witnessing</h2>\n<h3>Sharing personal testimony</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:29\">JHN 4:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:3-Acts22:8\">ACT 22:3–22:8</a> <em>Paul uses the account of his conversion in witnessing.</em></p>\n<h3>Explaining the Scriptures</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:30-Acts8:35\">ACT 8:30–8:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7-Isa53:8\">ISA 53:7–53:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:172\">PSA 119:172</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:1-Acts17:3\">ACT 17:1–17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:10-Acts17:12\">ACT 17:10–17:12</a></p>\n<h3>Using prophetic gifts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:24-1Cor14:25\">1CO 14:24–14:25</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Answering questions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:6\">COL 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:8-John9:11\">JHN 9:8–9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:15-John9:17\">JHN 9:15–9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:24-John9:25\">JHN 9:24–9:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Through writing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:31\">JHN 20:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:1-Luke1:4\">LUK 1:1–1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Through holy living</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:16\">MAT 5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:1-1Pet3:2\">1PE 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Through acts of devotion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:6-Matt26:7\">MAT 26:6–26:7</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:3\">MRK 14:3</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:36-Luke7:38\">LUK 7:36–7:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:1-John12:3\">JHN 12:1–12:3</a></p>\n<h2>The manner of witnessing</h2>\n<h3>With love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:15-Phil1:17\">PHP 1:15–1:17</a></p>\n<h3>With urgency</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:20\">2CO 5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:7-Ezek33:9\">EZK 33:7–33:9</a></p>\n<h3>Fearlessly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:19-Eph6:20\">EPH 6:19–6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:29\">ACT 4:29</a></p>\n<h3>Clearly and courteously</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:1-Acts26:3\">ACT 26:1–26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:4-Col4:6\">COL 4:4–4:6</a></p>",
